Gary Wallage Wedding Pro Theme

A custom high-performance WordPress theme built for the Gary Wallage Photography portfolio.

Key Features

Core: Lightweight, bloat-free layout engine.

Hero Slider: Custom center-mode circular carousel with 5 controllable slides.

Gallery Engine: Built-in Masonry, Square, Portrait, and Landscape grid layouts.

Visual Legacies: Custom Post Type integration for photo stories.

Performance: Automatic WebP conversion and LCP optimizations.

Customizer: Extensive options for Header, Footer, Hero, and Typography.

Structure

style.css - Main stylesheet (Grid, Typography, Layouts).

functions.php - Core logic (CPT registration, Customizer API, Performance hooks).

front-page.php - The Hero Carousel homepage template.

footer.php - 3-Column footer with Legal/Contact/Branding.

category.php & tag.php - Visual grid layouts for archives.

page-*.php - specialized templates for About, Services, FAQ.

Author

Gary Wallage Digital Ecosystem
